♪Love has no second chances♪

157
00:11:45,090 --> 00:11:48,880
♪I overrated myself♪

158
00:11:54,100 --> 00:11:58,370
♪When our stars cross paths again♪

159
00:11:58,600 --> 00:12:01,120
♪Perhaps it's destiny♪

160
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:05,570
♪A thousand encounters♪

161
00:12:05,880 --> 00:12:08,260
♪All lead to you♪

162
00:12:08,650 --> 00:12:11,910
♪My unreasonable demands♪

163
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:16,320
♪Are precious emotions to you♪

164
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:21,590
♪I'm sure I am your♪

165
00:12:21,810 --> 00:12:23,910
♪Only one♪

166
00:12:23,910 --> 00:12:27,360
♪I almost missed you♪

167
00:12:27,540 --> 00:12:30,930
♪No one can replace you♪

168
